Cops Beat Black Teen For “Resisting” His Jaywalking Ticket | Funs.co
A young black teenager was crossing the road in Stockton, CA when he was stopped by a cop. Cell phone footage shows a disturbing scene. Cenk Uygur, host of the The Young Turks, breaks it down. Tell us what you think in the comment section below.
“Video shows nine police California officers arrested a black teenager and slammed him on to concrete while arresting him for jaywalking.
Witnesses said a Stockton police officer ordered the teenager to sit down, but the teen instead continued walking toward a waiting bus, reported RT.”*
